node.text:
Not all heroes wear capes. Some wear cowboy hats. 🤠⁠
⁠
Yuhboi is responsible for these videos which shows their character shooting, tying up, and generally murdering figures in the game that are obviously dressed in KKK attire.⁠
⁠
🔗 Link in bio to read more
